<strong><a href="http://nwpermanente.com/wp-content/uploads/556bbe9f4214f808e7001193-2_thumbnail2x.jpg"><img class="alignleft wp-image-580" src="http://nwpermanente.com/wp-content/uploads/556bbe9f4214f808e7001193-2_thumbnail2x-150x150.jpg" alt="Sharon Meieran" width="80" height="76" /></a>Sharon Meieran</strong>, Emergency Medicine, Sunnyside Medical Center, recognized for her work in preventative health advocacy and emergency medicine.

