At Northwest Permanente, collegiality and collaboration are the foundation of our day-to-day interactions. Every year since 1979, NWP physicians have nominated peers who demonstrate professional excellence for the annual Distinguished Physician Award. The 8 award winners for 2020 were recognized for their dedication to their patients, peers, and communities. These physicians exemplify the best of Permanente Medicine.
<h3><strong>Meet the 2020 Distinguished Physician Award winners</strong></h3>
&nbsp;

