<strong>Tasha McDonald, MD, Radiation Oncology</strong>

<em>What her colleagues say about her: </em>"Dr. McDonald is the epitome of a physician who puts patients and her colleagues before herself. Everyone wants to be like her when they grow up. She is an excellent clinician, generous colleague, and a team player."

<em>From Dr. McDonald: </em>"Everybody's reason for doing what they're doing is different, although we all care for patients — we help people and heal people. Find your why, and you will succeed. When you get off track, remember your why. Patients fill my bucket — so that I can give to others in need."

